---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("December 28 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

// FAQ Schema data for AEO optimization
const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  mainEntity: []
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Year-In-Review: Our Commitment to the Shoals Community in 2027 | The Valley Clean Team"
  description="A look back at our year. Read about The Valley Clean Team's continued commitment to serving and giving back to the Shoals community in 2027."s continued commitment to serving and giving back to the Shoals community in 2027."
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Year-In-Review: Our Commitment to the Shoals Community in 2027"
    description="A look back at our year. Read about The Valley Clean Team's continued commitment to serving and giving back to the Shoals community in 2027."s continued commitment to serving and giving back to the Shoals community in 2027."s continued commitment to serving and giving back to the Shoals community in 2027."s continued commitment to serving and giving back to the Shoals community in 2027."
    publishDate="December 28 2026"
    author={author}
  />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Brand Story
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Year-In-Review: Our Commitment to the Shoals Community in 2027
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming December 28 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>December 28 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>How Has The Valley Clean Team Upheld Its Commitment to The Shoals Community in 2027?</h2>
<p><strong>In 2027, The Valley Clean Team has reinforced its dedication to The Shoals community by maintaining superior cleaning standards, supporting local initiatives, and enhancing client satisfaction through transparent practices. Our commitment is reflected in every spotless home and every community project we undertake.</strong></p>
<p>As a veteran and women-owned business, our values of precision, accountability, and community service have driven our operations in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas. Let's delve into the specifics of how we've stayed true to our mission this past year.</p>

<h3>Elevated Cleaning Standards: A Year of Unwavering Quality</h3>
<p>Throughout 2027, our cleaning specialists have consistently delivered exceptional service. Trained meticulously, they follow military-precision checklists ensuring every corner of your home is immaculate. This year, we:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Expanded Training Programs:</strong> We introduced advanced training sessions focusing on the latest cleaning technologies and techniques.</li>
  <li><strong>Implemented Systematic Audits:</strong> Regular audits were conducted to guarantee each service met our premium standards.</li>
  <li><strong>Enhanced Eco-Friendly Practices:</strong> We reduced our carbon footprint by integrating more sustainable cleaning products.</li>
</ul>
<p>These initiatives ensure that The Valley Clean Team remains synonymous with quality, offering a service that not only cleans but also restores and protects your home.</p>

<h3>Community Engagement: Strengthening Local Ties</h3>
<p>Our connection to The Shoals & Surrounding Areas goes beyond business. This year, we actively participated in local events and supported various community projects. Highlights include:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Local Sponsorships:</strong> We sponsored community sports teams and events, fostering local talent and encouraging community spirit.</li>
  <li><strong>Charity Initiatives:</strong> Partnering with local charities, we contributed both time and resources to support those in need.</li>
  <li><strong>Veteran Support Programs:</strong> As a veteran-owned business, we hosted workshops and offered mentorship to veterans transitioning to civilian careers.</li>
</ul>
<p>Our commitment to community engagement underscores our dedication to being more than just a cleaning service; we're a pivotal part of the local fabric.</p>

<h3>Transparency and Client Satisfaction: A Transparent Approach</h3>
<p>This year, we continued our transparent approach, ensuring our clients in The Shoals are well-informed and satisfied. Here's how we did it:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Upfront Pricing:</strong> Our clients appreciate clear pricing without hidden fees, starting at $125 for our premium services.</li>
  <li><strong>Open Communication:</strong> We maintained regular communication channels for feedback and service improvements.</li>
  <li><strong>Guaranteed Satisfaction:</strong> Our 100% satisfaction guarantee means we address any concerns promptly, ensuring our clients' peace of mind.</li>
</ul>
<p>Client satisfaction is our top priority, and in 2027, we have refined our processes to ensure every client feels valued and confident in our services.</p>

<h3>Looking Ahead: Continued Commitment to Excellence</h3>
<p>As we move beyond 2027, The Valley Clean Team pledges to uphold its mission of delivering unparalleled service and community support. Our focus will remain on:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Innovative Solutions:</strong> Continuously evolving to incorporate cutting-edge cleaning technologies.</li>
  <li><strong>Community Growth:</strong> Expanding our involvement in local initiatives to further enrich The Shoals & Surrounding Areas.</li>
  <li><strong>Client-Centric Services:</strong> Tailoring our services to meet the specific needs of each client, ensuring a personalized experience.</li>
</ul>
<p>By maintaining these commitments, we aim to exceed expectations and reinforce our reputation as the go-to cleaning specialists in The Shoals.</p>

<h3>Reclaim Your Time: Book Your Guaranteed Clean with The Valley Clean Team Today</h3>
<p>Don't let cleaning become a burden. Reclaim your time and enjoy a spotless home with our guaranteed cleaning services. <strong>Book your appointment today and experience the precision and professionalism that The Valley Clean Team is known for in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">December 28 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
